g.text: Use Case Diagram
Phase1
Phase2
US01 - 'bootstrap' user credential data for librarians
US02 - 'bootstrap' genre data
US03 - As Librarian I want to register an author 'name, short bio'
US04 - As Librarian I want to update an author’s data
US05 - As Librarian or Reader I want to know an author’s detail given its author number
US06 - As Librarian or Reader I want to search authors by name
US07 - As Librarian, I want to register a book
US08 - As Librarian I want to update a book’s data
US09 - As Librarian or Reader I want to know the details of a book given its ISBN
US10 - As Librarian or Reader I want to search books by genre
US11 - As anonymous I want to register as a reader
US12 - As Reader I want to update my personal data
US13 - As Librarian I want to know a user’s detail given its reader number
US14 - As Librarian I want to search Readers by name
US15 - As Librarian I want to lend a book to a reader
US16 - As Reader I want to return a book. If the return is overdue I’m fined by the library
US17 - As Reader or Librarian I want to know the details of a lending given its lending number
US01B - 'bootstrap' author and book data with meaningful data
US02B - 'bootstrap' lending data with meaningful data
US03B - As Librarian I want to register an author with an optional photo
US04B - As Reader I want to know the books of an Author
US05B - As Reader I want to know the co-authors of an author and their respective books
US06B - As Reader I want to know the Top 5 authors which have the most lent books
US07B - As Librarian, I want to register a book with a book cover photo
US08B - As Reader I want to search books by title
US09B - As Librarian I want to know the Top 5 books lent
US10B - As Librarian I want to know the Top 5 genres
US11B - As Librarian I want to know the Top 5 readers
US12B - As anonymous I want to register as a reader with an optional photo and list of interests
US13B - As Reader I want a list of book suggestions based on my interest list
US23 - As Librarian I want to list overdue lending sorted by their tardiness
US14B - As Librarian I want to know the average number of lending per genre of a certain month
US15B - As Librarian I want to know the Average lending duration
US16B - As Librarian I want to know the number of lendings per month for the last 12 months, broken down by genre
US17B - As Librarian I want to know the Top 5 readers per genre of a certain period
US18B - As Librarian I want to know the Monthly lending per reader of a certain period
US19B - As Librarian I want to know the Average lending duration Per genre per month for a certain period
